It's like, "Look at this; it's only God."Father, that the XRP would go to $100. Wouldn't that be amazing? Believe God for that.

01:54:39.860 --> 01:54:47.502
You look at XRP and you go to 100, XLM to some of these currencies and you go, "Man, it's like 20 bucks."And you go, "What?

01:54:47.503 --> 01:54:52.387
Look what the Lord did."Can you imagine that? Believe God for it.

01:54:52.388 --> 01:55:00.158
I've attached my faith out there that something major like that would happen. Wouldn't that be cool?

01:55:00.159 --> 01:55:10.382
You go in there and say, "Wow, look what the Lord did with XRP."Not financial advice, but in my opinion, that's what I'm believing for.

01:55:10.383 --> 01:55:16.122
What is Brandon looking for? That's what I'm believing for—that we would see some of these things go to over $100.

01:55:16.123 --> 01:55:24.944
And you look back and go, "Huh?"Wouldn't that be cool? We could build a massive auditorium for that, a massive ministry.

01:55:24.945 --> 01:55:36.479
We could do so much. The Lord could do so much. Not that I'm limiting him to it, but wouldn't that be cool?

01:55:36.480 --> 01:55:45.756
I don't know. It's cool to me in my world. Go to the moon, baby.

01:55:45.757 --> 01:55:55.357
You know, get viral with IRL. What he could get for people—get Solana to go to 10,000. Wouldn't that be cool?

01:55:55.358 --> 01:56:04.872
So you go on there and look at one morning you wake up and Solana is $10,000 per share and you go, "Look what the Lord did.

01:56:04.873 --> 01:56:15.168
It's Christmas."Wouldn't that be cool? I dream big. And most people say, "Brandon, you're out of it, man."I don't know.

01:56:15.169 --> 01:56:21.824
I just know God is big. And you say it's just as big a miracle as an arm growing out.

01:56:21.825 --> 01:56:28.409
Some of you have been living at the bottom of the barrel and the barrel's on top of you, to be able to wake up one day...

01:56:28.410 --> 01:56:36.559
and he said, remember what he said? The Lord just remember, he said, "I told you that I'll make decamillionaires overnight.

01:56:36.560 --> 01:56:43.279
I'll make decillionaires overnight, Brandon, in a 24-hour period. Everything is going to change.

01:56:43.280 --> 01:56:52.959
I can change your circumstance in a 24-hour period."That's what he said to me. "I'll make you a decillionaire overnight."I said, "How?

01:56:52.960 --> 01:57:02.051
How?"I don't mean to challenge you—I know you can—but really you could do that for me?

01:57:02.052 --> 01:57:13.118
Why not? Why not me? Why not you? He's no respecter of persons, ladies and gentlemen.

01:57:13.119 --> 01:57:19.118
And then he tells me, "You're not believing big enough."I'll close with this.

01:57:19.119 --> 01:57:29.139
Anybody remember whenever I was taken out of my body and I was taken to the universe and I'm standing there with the Father?

01:57:29.140 --> 01:57:39.518
I cannot see Jesus's face, but he is standing there talking about the distance between the sun and the earth.

01:57:39.519 --> 01:57:47.185
He said light travels at 186,000 miles per second and takes about eight minutes to get there.

01:57:47.186 --> 01:58:04.065
He was explaining every planet, how far it was, how close the nearest star was, and how many light-years it takes traveling at 186,000 miles per second to get to the nearest star.

01:58:04.066 --> 01:58:19.591
He said, "You have all these things, from Saturn to Venus to all these planets and all this creation that he has made for every one of us, and we don't even live in outer space."But it was so big and huge.

01:58:19.592 --> 01:58:29.021
It takes 8 minutes and 20 seconds for light to travel from the sun to the Earth.

01:58:29.022 --> 01:58:34.267
Traveling at 186,000 miles per second, that is incredible.

01:58:34.268 --> 01:58:46.158
He took me to a room in another dimension and said it was still being created.

01:58:46.159 --> 01:59:14.075
I could see this white room where creation was the size of a car, moving at 186,000 miles per second—either that or it was the speed of sound, I don't know—but it was moving slowly, barely creeping as he spoke it.

01:59:14.076 --> 01:59:23.629
It was moving in all directions, and I could see it expanding.

01:59:23.630 --> 01:59:39.279
I saw planets, lights, and stars all being thrown into space right in front of me.

01:59:39.280 --> 01:59:43.798
He took it and shrunk it down in front of my face and put it in his hands.

01:59:43.799 --> 01:59:51.302
He said, "I can hold the universe in the palm of my hands, Brandon.

01:59:51.303 --> 01:59:58.479
I can stretch it out and make it bigger, and I have control over the whole thing.

01:59:58.480 --> 02:00:08.319
But the closest star to you—how close was it, Braden?"He told me exactly, but I don't remember.

02:00:08.320 --> 02:00:28.110
It was Alpha Centauri or something like that. It takes 4.37 light-years traveling at 186,000 miles per second to get there.

02:00:28.111 --> 02:00:48.368
That's a long way. He took it all in front of my face. I saw how vast it was—billions and billions, if not trillions, of stars.

02:00:48.369 --> 02:00:56.959
There are as many as there are grains of sand on all the beaches of the world.

02:00:56.960 --> 02:01:07.169
It would take over four, almost five years at the speed of light to travel that distance.

02:01:07.170 --> 02:01:17.837
He showed me how vast and big he truly is, and how he can control and manipulate it in his hand.

02:01:17.838 --> 02:01:37.680
He said, "Brandon, I want to show you this."I could see it being molded and shaped, and he said, "I have power and authority over all of it."At the end of this visitation, he took me to the edge of where heaven and earth meet.

02:01:37.681 --> 02:01:49.269
He said, "Braden, this is the tithe. This is my kingdom, but I have given all of this to my kids.

02:01:49.270 --> 02:02:00.936
I kept ten percent for myself—I am doing simple math for you so you can comprehend it—but I've given the rest to you.

02:02:00.937 --> 02:02:11.039
At the end of the thousand years, you will rule and reign over the galaxies in the universe.

02:02:11.040 --> 02:02:28.608
Every one of my kids who is born again will get their own galaxy like the Milky Way, and every single one of you will rule and reign with me for eternity.

02:02:28.609 --> 02:02:35.342
Every one of you has the ability to create with your words, for you were made in my image.

02:02:35.343 --> 02:02:54.271
As he is, so are we in this world, and we are able to create with our words."He said life and death are in the power of the tongue, and after the thousand years, you'll rule and reign with me forever.

02:02:54.272 --> 02:03:07.493
He said, "Brandon, I created all those planets and stars for my kids to rule and reign over.

02:03:07.494 --> 02:03:22.793
Tell my people, Brandon, to believe me for bigger, for I am a big God."I shot back into my bed and screamed.

02:03:22.794 --> 02:03:45.399
Diana said, "What did you see this time, honey?"I said, "I saw how big God is and how he controls everything in the palm of his hand."He said, "My people don't believe me for big enough,"but I could see the vastness of how big he truly is.

02:03:45.400 --> 02:03:55.172
He creates things, and so many people are scared about their bills or food.

02:03:55.173 --> 02:04:11.643
He said, "Take no thought of what you wear; take no thought of this stuff, because I know what you need before you even know you need it."Some people say the earth is flat.

02:04:11.644 --> 02:04:19.276
The earth is not flat. I know I tick a lot of you off, but the earth is round.

02:04:19.277 --> 02:04:42.121
I saw it; I was with him and I watched it all happen. A lot of you have been fed poison. You say it's in the Bible, but it's not that way. I saw it.

02:04:42.122 --> 02:04:55.711
The earth is the Lord's and the fullness thereof, and he has given it to the sons of men.

02:04:55.712 --> 02:04:59.455
After the thousand years, you are going to have your own galaxy.

02:04:59.456 --> 02:05:04.615
Some say, "That's Mormonism, Brandon,"but I'm not lining up with the Mormon faith.

02:05:04.616 --> 02:05:23.198
I'm telling you what the Father said. It was amazing. I saw purples, pinks, and all kinds of beautiful colors at the edge of heaven.

02:05:23.199 --> 02:05:34.838
It is absolutely beautiful. God is as big as your faith will allow him to be.

02:05:34.839 --> 02:05:47.617
You need to learn to believe him for bigger. In him there is no end and no beginning; he is endless.

02:05:47.618 --> 02:06:20.915
He is his own dimension. We are made in his image. He is light, and that light is his skin. As you go into it, he is beautiful beyond description.

02:06:20.916 --> 02:06:34.158
I don't care what you believe; I feel sorry for you if you think too small and are bound by your own mind.

02:06:34.159 --> 02:06:43.759
You have to think bigger. To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

02:06:43.760 --> 02:07:00.902
He is awesome. Don't stay in your little religious box. Believe God for bigger.

02:07:00.903 --> 02:07:06.879
He has exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

02:07:06.880 --> 02:07:43.039
Stretch your capacity to believe him for more. Heaven is ginormous—it's bigger than Jupiter.

02:07:43.040 --> 02:08:06.609
It is a massive place. People say the Holy City is 1,500 miles wide, but that's just the city where his throne room is.

02:08:06.610 --> 02:08:15.378
That's not all of heaven; it's just one area. Heaven is massive. God doesn't do little.

02:08:15.379 --> 02:08:21.118
He doesn't think little, and he doesn't have little in his vocabulary.

02:08:21.119 --> 02:08:30.718
His thinking. He's a big God with big plans. And it's like Oral Roberts says, 'Make no little plans here.

02:08:30.719 --> 02:08:39.630
Believe God for bigger.'If I can just get a brand new Honda—nothing wrong with a Honda—but God wants you to believe him for bigger.

02:08:39.631 --> 02:08:49.999
Believe him for more and more in 2026. Believe God because I'm telling you, he can take it and he is a creator.

02:08:50.000 --> 02:08:56.152
His words don't return to void. They grow into things and they grow plants in front of him.

02:08:56.153 --> 02:09:09.919
I've seen it and I watch him and I marvel at him. He is amazing. I've seen him transform, and I can see fire in his eye.

02:09:09.920 --> 02:09:18.158
It's just like I look at things and I go, 'Man.'I told you he's looking at things and he said, 'I'm watching you.

02:09:18.159 --> 02:09:25.352
I'm watching you.'I tell you these things in my experiences, but I have private things all the time.

02:09:25.353 --> 02:09:37.999
I'm telling you, he is vast. He looks like he could melt you, but he's love.

02:09:38.000 --> 02:09:48.800
He's powerful and I fear him. I fear him. I told Dee, 'He scares me.'Nobody has a clue.

02:09:48.801 --> 02:09:56.128
They think if you die, nobody knows the truth. I'm telling you, God is scary.

02:09:56.129 --> 02:10:12.314
He's powerful. It is beyond our human comprehension. Our little peanut brains try to figure it out.

02:10:12.315 --> 02:10:27.508
God is vast. I tried to be as real with these people as I can. Heresy! Throw an egg at him and stone him.

02:10:27.509 --> 02:10:40.126
You'll see when you get there and you're going to go, 'Oh my gosh, Brandon, you were right.'I don't want to be arrogant, but I say, 'Yeah, I know.

02:10:40.127 --> 02:10:50.715
I tried to tell you. It's all Jesus.'I tried to warn you. He's big and he's really cool.

02:10:50.716 --> 02:10:59.476
Everything is amazing. He has all this stuff for us and he loves us so much.

02:10:59.477 --> 02:11:07.602
His kingdom is vast and his streets are gold and his houses he's made—all of it is just amazing.

02:11:07.603 --> 02:11:17.439
There isn't anything ugly. He's a good God and his ability is beyond anything you can comprehend.

02:11:17.440 --> 02:11:22.235
That's why I'm trying to tell you all tonight. The theme of this was: believe God for bigger.

02:11:22.236 --> 02:11:36.127
He said, 'Tell my people to believe me for more. They think too small.'He wanted to show me how big he was, how far the stars were.

02:11:36.128 --> 02:11:53.634
He took me and he showed me, but he said, 'Brandon, what's going to be amazing is you'll travel at the speed of thought, no longer by the speed of light.'He said that's slow.

02:11:53.635 --> 02:12:04.509
He just reminded me that the speed of light is slow. I saw things moving and being created.

02:12:04.510 --> 02:12:07.517
Stars are forming and it was all still being created right now.

02:12:07.518 --> 02:12:18.399
It's never stopped and it's still being done right now, going in all different directions.

02:12:18.400 --> 02:12:29.778
Can you tell me which way's north in the universe? You can't say due north star, but I'm talking about when it's all vast.

02:12:29.779 --> 02:12:40.479
It's still being created in all different directions. And it's all being thrown into the lights and the stars and all of it.

02:12:40.480 --> 02:13:03.359
It's amazing. I watched him doing it. I was like, 'Lord,'and he said, 'I can measure it in my hand, son.'But he chose to love each one of us.

02:13:03.360 --> 02:13:21.350
What is man that you are mindful of him? Why do you look our direction? 'I love you. I died for you.

02:13:21.351 --> 02:13:35.999
I suffered for you gravely that none of you should perish, that all come to repentance.'If you're here tonight and you don't know Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal savior, you're running out of time.

02:13:36.000 --> 02:13:43.118
It's appointed unto man once to die and after that the judgment.

02:13:43.119 --> 02:14:02.479
I want you tonight to really search your heart and really ask yourself, 'Do I know him?'And more importantly, 'Does he know me?'If I were to die tonight, would I get to spend eternity with him?

02:14:02.480 --> 02:14:07.162
It's not your grandma's religion. It's not your mama's. It's you.

02:14:07.163 --> 02:14:13.752
Do you know Jesus? Nobody else is going to bring you to heaven.

02:14:13.753 --> 02:14:19.198
Their prayers have brought you here to this point, but I'm telling you, it's your choice.

02:14:19.199 --> 02:14:28.685
There's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun tonight. Do you know my friend Jesus? You may come and say, 'Brandon, I don't know him.

02:14:28.686 --> 02:14:39.152
I'm here tonight and I think you're kooky or whatever, but inside I know there's some truth to what you're saying.'I feel that tugging.

02:14:39.153 --> 02:14:52.078
But the Bible says, 'No man comes to the Father unless he's drawn by him.'If there is any kind of doubt inside of your heart that if you were to die tonight, where would you spend eternity?

02:14:52.079 --> 02:14:59.027
The very shoes you put on today to go to work, the undertaker might be taking them off tonight.

02:14:59.028 --> 02:15:08.898
No man knows the day he's going to die. And we're not promised tomorrow. I'm going to be real with you.

02:15:08.899 --> 02:15:16.078
You could die right now, but if you did, where would you spend eternity?

02:15:16.079 --> 02:15:22.833
Don't gamble with your future. Well, 'I don't believe it at all.'That's your problem.

02:15:22.834 --> 02:15:28.150
It doesn't change anything just because you don't believe it.

02:15:28.151 --> 02:15:34.664
The Bible's true. And no man comes to the Father except through Jesus Christ.

02:15:34.665 --> 02:15:41.999
It's not Muhammad. It's not Buddha. Jesus is the only way to heaven. Period.

02:15:42.000 --> 02:15:47.598
The Bible's true and everything that the world's trying to tell you is a lie.

02:15:47.599 --> 02:15:56.238
This is the only truth: the B-I-B-L-E. This was written inspired by the Holy Ghost.

02:15:56.239 --> 02:16:06.356
So I want you tonight to search your heart right now. We're going to close this thing out. You can go about your business.

02:16:06.357 --> 02:16:18.154
But I want you to right now search your heart and ask, 'Does he know me?'And if you don't, I want you to put in the comment section right now, 'I need to be saved.

02:16:18.155 --> 02:16:26.077
I want to repent. I want to come to Jesus tonight.'I want to make a new, clean start tonight.

02:16:26.078 --> 02:16:41.119
Tonight's my night. I'm coming home. This might be your last chance. So, I'm going to say a simple prayer.

02:16:41.120 --> 02:16:58.478
I know people say, 'Brandon, it's with the mouth confession is made.'But what I'm trying to say is that confession is made out of the heart.

02:16:58.479 --> 02:17:19.119
What you're saying out of your heart is a heart thing. I need to memorize scripture better, but what I'm trying to tell you is that confession is made with your heart.

02:17:19.120 --> 02:17:32.081
Say it with all your heart. 'I believe you are the Son of God. I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.'Father, I believe.

02:17:32.082 --> 02:17:40.835
Father Jesus, tonight I repent of my sins. I believe you are the Son of God.

02:17:40.836 --> 02:17:49.037
I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day. Jesus, from this day forward, I turn my back on the world.

02:17:49.038 --> 02:17:56.583
I turn my back on the devil. I turn my back on my sin. And I ask you to forgive me.

02:17:56.584 --> 02:18:07.678
I ask you to wash me. Make me clean and new. From this day forward, Lord, I serve you all the rest I have.

02:18:07.679 --> 02:18:14.067
I make you my Lord and personal Savior. Thank you, Lord, that I'm made new today.

02:18:14.068 --> 02:18:21.946
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life. I dedicate my life to you, Father.

02:18:21.947 --> 02:18:29.839
And I thank you, Lord, that you've forgiven me tonight and you're giving me a fresh, clean start.

02:18:29.840 --> 02:18:35.663
I've messed up a whole lot, and I thank you, Lord, that you've forgiven me of it.

02:18:35.664 --> 02:18:46.697
And today, I'm made new. I'll serve you from this day forward, Lord, in the mighty name of Jesus. Amen and amen.

02:18:46.698 --> 02:18:54.638
I believe if you just said that prayer, you just gave your heart to Jesus Christ and you're born again.

02:18:54.639 --> 02:19:02.531
'Behold, I make all things new,'he says. As far as the east is from the west, he's taken your sins from you.

02:19:02.532 --> 02:19:07.275
Today, I believe you just got born again. Welcome to the family.

02:19:07.276 --> 02:19:17.759
We love you. We pray for you. Now, the moment you confessed your sin is when you got rid of it.

02:19:17.760 --> 02:19:27.676
You said, 'Well, Brandon, I was messed up.'Yep. So was I. We were all sinners here. Nobody's here to judge you.

02:19:27.677 --> 02:19:34.816
We're just here to love on you and tell you, "Hey, He has a plan for your life."We're all sinners.

02:19:34.817 --> 02:19:42.558
That's all. But every one of us did the same thing you just did.

02:19:42.559 --> 02:19:49.119
And I'm telling you, it was the best decision I've ever made, giving my heart to Jesus Christ.

02:19:49.120 --> 02:19:53.577
Now, what do you do? You go to a Bible-believing church. Find a Bible.

02:19:53.578 --> 02:20:01.580
Read your Bible every day. I want you to come and pray with us over here. Tell the pastor there at that church.

02:20:01.581 --> 02:20:11.754
When you find a Bible-believing church—a non-denominational one is what I'd find—tell them, "I need to be water-baptized."Get water-baptized.

02:20:11.755 --> 02:20:16.747
Get plugged into that church. Find a small group, whatever they have there.

02:20:16.748 --> 02:20:24.567
Get plugged in with believers. Get excited about what you did here today. The best is yet to come. You know what?

02:20:24.568 --> 02:20:29.078
If you fall down and the devil starts to remind you of your past, remind him of his future.

02:20:29.079 --> 02:20:34.781
He's about ready to burn in hell forever and ever. He's going to get cast into the lake of fire.

02:20:34.782 --> 02:20:40.434
It's coming. It's coming sooner than later. I'm telling you, folks, Jesus Christ is coming. Welcome to the family.

02:20:40.435 --> 02:20:46.992
I don't know how many people gave their hearts to Jesus, if any, but even if there was only one, we're excited for you.

02:20:46.993 --> 02:20:57.896
If you don't have a Bible and you would like one, email us down below and we will send you a Bible for free just to celebrate your decision tonight.

02:20:57.897 --> 02:21:06.753
The email is down below. Say, "Welcome to the family. Welcome to the decision that you made."Do we know how many?

02:21:06.754 --> 02:21:12.258
34 people. Welcome all 34 of you that gave your heart to Jesus Christ tonight.

02:21:12.259 --> 02:21:17.877
I'm excited about every single one of you. Diana is too; she's filling out all the things.

02:21:17.878 --> 02:21:22.159
We've been slamming busy with so many people getting saved on all our channels.

02:21:22.160 --> 02:21:26.913
We're excited about every single one of you. Welcome to the family.

02:21:26.914 --> 02:21:31.167
All 34 of you gave your heart to Jesus Christ. That's a good little altar call.

02:21:31.168 --> 02:21:39.316
That's exciting. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us tonight.

02:21:39.317 --> 02:21:50.773
I'll never ask you for anything other than this: if you could like, subscribe, click the notification bell, click the like button, and comment something nice down below, it helps with the algorithm.

02:21:50.774 --> 02:21:55.072
I'm so thankful that they didn't pull our live stream tonight.

02:21:55.073 --> 02:22:00.036
It started a little bit when you were talking about Edward Snowden, but it stopped.

02:22:00.037 --> 02:22:05.554
They almost pulled a daring Edward Snowden; that was a warning, but they didn't get it.

02:22:05.555 --> 02:22:09.535
All glory to Jesus. Isn't that wonderful? They didn't pull my thing.

02:22:09.536 --> 02:22:14.271
They tried to do it last night three times. They did not like me talking about the mafia.

02:22:14.272 --> 02:22:22.500
I said, "Well, we touched a nerve there, but we're thankful for their platform, aren't we?"Isn't it wonderful they allow us to do this?

02:22:22.501 --> 02:22:31.890
It's all glory to Jesus, you know, but we're on their thing until somebody comes up with something better that people go to.

02:22:31.891 --> 02:22:37.996
It's not about just going on a platform; we need traffic. The unsaved are who we're after.

02:22:37.997 --> 02:22:49.484
The Lord said, "Brendon, I'm not going after the saved; I'm going for those who are lost."There are so many people trying to fish in their own backyard, like in their own little aquarium here.

02:22:49.485 --> 02:22:54.799
We have to go after the people in the byways and the highways and everywhere else.

02:22:54.800 --> 02:23:00.005
There are people going to hell that need to know Jesus Christ is coming.

02:23:00.006 --> 02:23:07.056
These platforms like this—what's the traffic over here? Millions of people come on YouTube.

02:23:07.057 --> 02:23:15.919
Thank God for YouTube. God is using it, and X, and all these others.

02:23:15.920 --> 02:23:19.382
I know that was a little different tonight, but that's what the Lord wanted to do.

02:23:19.383 --> 02:23:32.973
God bless it. We'll see you again soon, I guess tomorrow. 2.7 billion monthly active users globally.

02:23:32.974 --> 02:23:45.154
Think about that. 2.7 billion monthly active users on YouTube.

02:23:45.155 --> 02:23:59.074
3.1 billion by year's end, attracting nearly half the world's internet users with India leading in users and Saudi Arabia having the highest percentage.

02:23:59.075 --> 02:24:16.639
Users spend significant time on the platform viewing billions of videos, and the user base continues strong growth.

02:24:16.640 --> 02:24:28.398
Isn't that amazing? That's incredible to me. 3.1 billion by year's end.

02:24:28.399 --> 02:24:35.591
That's why we're excited about this platform because we have—what is it, 5,000? That's not very good.

02:24:35.592 --> 02:24:43.722
Whenever you have 3.1 billion, 6,000—we have a lot more opportunity to grow, don't we?

02:24:43.723 --> 02:24:52.171
So, we're believing God for a million subscribers. We're believing for over 100,000 people praying at a time.

02:24:52.172 --> 02:25:03.469
We have not even 10% of what I'm believing for, for us all to pray at the same time and wreak havoc on the devil.

02:25:03.470 --> 02:25:10.793
He hates these live prayer things. God bless it. Thank you for joining us and we'll see you again, probably tomorrow.

02:25:10.794 --> 02:25:20.155
I want to pray over the thing for New Year's Eve. We're almost there, closing this year out and finishing strong.

02:25:20.156 --> 02:25:26.045
Taking communion and praying. Who wants to join me for New Year's Eve? I'll just pray for a little bit.

02:25:26.046 --> 02:25:32.079
I'm going to really pray over that day and see what we do, but maybe the day before or whatever.

02:25:32.080 --> 02:25:35.741
Tomorrow's it. We only have two more days. 2025 is over, baby.

02:25:35.742 --> 02:25:46.918
We'll put that on the shelf. God bless you all. We love you. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:25:46.919 --> 02:25:55.154
Jesus loves you and we love you. We'll see you again soon. Bye-bye.

